                            Label: "leave_button"
                        }
                    ],
                    Texts: [
                        {
                            Text: "I study the cold as it is - soft light on the drifts, sharp teeth beneath. Care to give me a reading, in the way of battle?"
                        },
                        {
                            Text: "Last warden of the frost. Beat me and the apprentice will see you. Ready?"
                        },
                        {
                            Text: "For the record, the Leader owns a coat. I have measured the coat. It is a good coat. The people in this gym need hobbies."
                        },
                        {
                            Text: "The lights over town are not named after me. I checked the dates twice. It is a coincidence, and I decline to discuss it further."
                        }
                    ],
                    Name: "Aurora - warden of the inner runs",
                    Label: "default"
                }
            ]
